{"tid":859923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【假受害女星真講大話】無辜監製Harvey先勝一仗 其中一項性侵罪獲撤控","createTime":"2018-10-13T02:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T04:18:32.000Z","uid":32051,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa1fb25263bf8b31566b7b2447a96f673107fd5","tid":859923,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"荷里活單純監製Harvey Weinstein被多名女星指控性侵，仲引發#MeToo風暴，不過佢其中一單被控嘅性侵罪就獲撤銷，原因就係假受害女星Lucia Evans講大話！<br />\n<br />\n美國時間周四，紐約法庭正式撤控Harvey Weinstein其中一條性侵罪，原因係3個控告佢嘅女星之一Lucia Evans講大話。佢原本控告Harvey於2004年喺辦公室被逼為男方口交，當時Lucia只係21歲嘅學生。但其後於私人信件中，發現Lucia承認口交行為係雙方願意，目的為幫女方發展演藝事業。另外，一名探員又被揭曾干擾證人，叫對方唔好講出對辯方有利嘅證供，因此法官就撤銷Lucia嘅案件，但Harvey仍然面對另外兩名女性嘅指控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n司法勝利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/103641_f9d632f978a10c9217462c9eb66da7d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F103641_f9d632f978a10c9217462c9eb66da7d9.png&h=9d79bf95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講大話作假口供的Lucia Evans<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/103945_8473059f0db0587762f381557b9d82e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F103945_8473059f0db0587762f381557b9d82e0.png&h=bda3b592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n性侵案受害人監製<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果妓者我屌你老母</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181012/58785716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58785716&d=ebHhyD